These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, pepper, potato
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, helicopter, roller
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, musician, designer
1. the person eating pepper is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the pilot##2
2. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
3. the musician is on the right of the pilot##1
4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Food          | corn      | pepper        | potato     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| Transport   | helicopter   | trike       | roller |
| Job         | pilot  | musician      | designer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, coach, photographer
House: modern, gothic-revival, townhouse
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, swisher, ritmeester
1. the modern house is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the coach##1
3. the modern house is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the coach is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the photographer is in an even position##4
7. the ritmeester-smoker is between the gothic-revival house and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | coach    | photographer | accountant |
| House   | gothic-revival | modern       | townhouse   |
| Pet           | hamster  | guinea-pig   | ferret     |
| Cigar         | swisher | ritmeester       | vegafina   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower, iris
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, turtle
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, indie
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
2. the person who growsiris is the fan of indie##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the person who growsazalea is between the person watching adventure movies and the fan of indie##2
5. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the turtle is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Flower          | iris | azalea | sunflower |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | action | adventure |
| Pet           | pony       | bird   | turtle    |
| Music-Genre     | indie      | electronic   | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking
City: miami, rome, berlin
House: townhouse, futuristic, tower
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, pakistani
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is the futuristic house##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Hobby         | photography  | chess       | woodworking |
| City           | berlin     | rome      | miami   |
| House   | futuristic | townhouse | tower     |
| Nationality   | british      | pakistani   | italian     |

