.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, water
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, august
City: san-francisco, hamburg, berlin
There are 3 different nationalities: german, mexican, polish
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the german##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the polish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | water     | juice   | coffee         |
| Birthday           | february | november | august |
| City   | berlin      | hamburg   | san-francisco            |
| Nationality   | mexican   | polish  | german         |

