.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cauliflower, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, photographer, social-worker
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, boat
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, tea
1. the person driving the bus is between the photographer and the person eating cauliflower##2
2. the person drinking cola is the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person driving the boat is the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the social-worker##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Food          | raspberry    | asparagus     | cauliflower |
| Job           | photographer | social-worker | doctor      |
| Transport   | boat      | bus       | quad-bike    |
| Beverage   | lemonade      | cola         | tea     |

