House: craftsman, gothic-revival, futuristic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, metal, r&b
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, taxi
1. the british is in the middle##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the british##1
3. the futuristic house is the person driving the roller##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
5. the italian is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the fan of ambient is between the person driving the roller and the german##2
7. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Nationality          | german | british | italian |
| House   | gothic-revival  | craftsman    | futuristic |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | ambient   | r&b    |
| Transport     | taxi   | car       | roller |

