City: venice, nizza, edinburgh
1. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the dressmaker##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the pakistani##1
6. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is between the pakistani and the person traveling to edinburgh##2

