House: cape-cod, cottage, gothic-revival
1. the colombian is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
3. the turkish is the cape-cod house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the colombian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the turkish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | apricot  | cabbage   | lemon      |
| Hobby   | drawing    | collecting      | dancing      |
| Nationality   | canadian | colombian | turkish    |
| House           | gothic-revival   | cottage     | cape-cod |

