.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-10::.
House: art-deco, cottage, gothic-revival
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, electronic, indie
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, japanese, thai
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, satire
1. the japanese is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the fan of classical is the art-deco house##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of classical is the thai##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
7. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| House           | art-deco     | gothic-revival    | cottage |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | electronic | indie      |
| Nationality   | thai       | japanese   | chinese    |
| Movie-Genre     | mystery | satire        | thriller     |

