.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, photographer, mechanic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, horror
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, horse
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, van, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the van##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
7. the photographer is between the software-developer and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Job      | mechanic       | photographer   | software-developer |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | disaster |
| Pet           | bird      | chinchilla | horse    |
| Transport         | van  | quad-bike     | bus |

