.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, analyst, fisherman
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, dancing, camping
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, apricot, white
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, trike
1. the accountant is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the accountant is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the analyst is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes ebony is the person driving the trike##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
8. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | accountant | analyst   | fisherman |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | dancing    | camping    |
| Color         | apricot    | ebony | white   |
| Transport     | motorbike  | trike     | airplane  |

