.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, video-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, crime, scientific
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, soy-milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, rowing
1. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person watching scientific movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby         | video-games    | reading   | puzzles      |
| Movie-Genre           | scientific | sports    | crime |
| Beverage   | tea       | lemonade | soy-milk      |
| Sport         | rowing         | parkour   | climbing     |

