.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-16::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, peas, tomato
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, epic, family
3 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, bridge
3 different pets are kept: snake, cat, guinea-pig
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Food          | peas     | pear   | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | epic   | drama      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | canasta | bridge    |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | snake   | cat |

