There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, white, pink
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, dutch, pakistani
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, june, december
1. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating nectarine and the person who's birthday is in december##2
3. the colombian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes white##1
6. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Food          | onion     | cauliflower | nectarine   |
| Color         | pink   | azure | white |
| Nationality   | pakistani | dutch       | colombian   |
| Birthday     | december     | september  | june        |

