The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, filmmaking
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, police-officer, security-guard
There 3 different types of food: avocado, pineapple, lettuce
1. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the police-officer is between the security-guard and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating avocado##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2        |     3      |
| Sport      | volleyball         | badminton         | climbing       |
| Hobby         | chess          | camping        | filmmaking |
| Job           | security-guard | police-officer | doctor     |
| Food   | avocado      | pineapple          | lettuce     |

