.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, cranberry, lettuce
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, indie, punk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, game, old-henry
3 different pets are kept: snake, rat, goat
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
4. the owner of the goat is the person eating lettuce##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the fan of house is the game-smoker##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating cranberry is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Food          | cranberry  | apricot   | lettuce |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | punk      | house   |
| Cigar   | ritmeester     | old-henry | game |
| Pet         | rat | snake   | goat   |

