.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, horror, action
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, rock
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
6. the person watching action movies is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Movie-Genre           | epic  | action | horror   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | rock           | disco      |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate   | almond-milk          | iced-tea |
| Transport     | boat    | tram           | snowmobile |

 